  "content": "eight: 800; color: var(--accent-purple);\">NVIDIA dGPU</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n        RTX 3060 Laptop<br>CUDA 12.8 / cuDNN 9.2<br>6 GB VRAM\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- What we're testing -->\n  <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-blue);\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-blue); margin-bottom: 12px;\">Model Under Test</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700;\">nomic-embed-text-v1.5</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 6px;\">\n      ~137M parameters &bull; 768 dimensions &bull; ONNX format &bull; via fastembed-rs\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>All three backends use the same ONNX Runtime — only the execution provider differs. Same model, same code path, different hardware.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">02 / 08</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 3: WHERE THE TIME GOES — visual waterfall with measured data -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">Where The Time Goes</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    I Instrumented<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-amber\">Every Stage.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    Most benchmarks show total latency. I added per-stage timing to the server\n    to see where time is actually spent. Here's a typical request on CUDA.\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Waterfall chart — visual timeline of a ~106ms request -->\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    <!-- Scale bar -->\n    <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0 180px 0 160px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted);\">0ms</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted);\">50ms</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted);\">106ms</span>\n    </div>",
